Mypy Fix Report for src/__main__.py
Date: 2026-07-01

Summary
- Resolved all 14 reported mypy errors by correcting typing usage in Engine.
- Main causes were:
  - Mixing model-name string type with LLM object type.
  - Treating Pydantic models as dictionaries.
  - Assuming encode() indexing/toList behavior without stable typing.

Detailed Mapping (error -> fix)

1) Line 33: Incompatible types in assignment (Small_LLM_Model vs str)
- Problem:
